
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HOME PAGE</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <%- include('../backend/inc/header.ejs'); -%>
    <style>
        .btn-login{
            background-color: #332E7C;
            border-radius: 0%;
            color: #fff;
            transition: all 0.5s;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        .btn-login:hover{
            background-color: #332E7C;
            border-radius: 0%;
            color: #fff;
            border-color: 1px #fff;
        }
        .btn-login span {
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-block;
            position: relative;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }
        .btn-login span:after {
            content: '\00bb';
            position: absolute;
            opacity: 0;
            top: 0;
            right: -20px;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }
        .btn-login:hover span {padding-right: 25px;}
        .btn-login:hover span:after {opacity: 1;right: 0;}
    </style>
</head>
<body class="container">
        <div class="card card-header text-center">
            <img src="img/logo.png" width="80">
            <h1>ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບສູ່ລະບົບເກັບຄ່ານ້ຳປະປາ ຂອງບ້ານພູໂຮມໄຊ</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="card card-body">
            <div class="form-group text-center">
                <a href="/<%=admin%>" class="btn btn-login"> <span>ເຂົ້າສູ່ລະບົບ </span> </a>
            </div>
        </div>
</body>
</html>